[SN]TITLE[SN]
Sheffield Steelers beat Cardiff Devils to win Elite League play-offs

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Sheffield Steelers won the Elite League play-offs 6-5 in second overtime to deny Cardiff Devils a grand slam.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
